content: As an AI language model, I do not have opinions or the ability to predict the future. However, there are always strong teams that can challenge Real Madrid's record in the Champions League. Nevertheless, it's challenging to dominate the Champions League for years, as it involves several factors such as squad depth, tactics, team morale, etc.
